[2] WHO update 16 Apr 2014 - 1 case, Hunan
Date: 16 Apr 2014
Source: WHO Global Alert and Response - 16 Apr 2014 [edited]
http://who.int/csr/don/2014_04_16_h7n9/en/


On [15 Apr 2014], the National Health and Family Planning Commission (NHFPC) of China notified WHO of an additional laboratory-confirmed case of human infection with avian influenza A(H7N9) virus.

The patient is a 30-year-old man from Hengyang City, Hunan Province. He became ill on [9 Apr 2014], was admitted to a hospital on [13 Apr 2014] and is currently in a stable condition.

--
